Class RationalState

java.lang.Object
BESA.Kernel.Agent.StateBESA
rational.RationalState
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class RationalState extends BESA.Kernel.Agent.StateBESA
RationalState is a class that extends StateBESA, representing the state of a rational agent. It contains information about the agent's believes, main role, synchronous and asynchronous services, and subscriptions to update.
